    "This is because the size of predictions used for knowledge distillation is much smaller than that of model updates utilized for aggregation.",
    "Fig. 7 plots the test accuracy and communication overhead with respect to the communication round.",
    "It is observed that our Selective-FD method has comparable or inferior accuracy to FedAvg.",
    "But it considerably improves communication efficiency during federated training.",
    "Further improving the performance of Selective-FD is a promising direction for future research."
